kpi.name: M1002C666

kpi_info.title: HS-DSCH ALLO FOR SRB IN SRNC
kpi_info.use: The number of successful HS-DSCH allocations for Signalling Radio Bearer in the SRNC. UPDATED:When the RNC receives RRC: RADIO BEARER RECONFIGURATION COMPLETE message or other RRC protocol acknowledgement message from the UE after a successful HS-DSCH allocation for SRB. This can happen either in an initial allocation, serving cell change, incoming hard handover or channel type switch.
